race.comment: SHE'S FEARLESS (2) posted a superb 24.53 winning over 440m at this track last start. Top win latest and looms as the one to beat again. ZIPPING XADEN (1) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his lightning win the start prior, getting around Wentworth Park over 520m in 29.40. Should be in this for a long way. TAW GALAXY (6) is looking to continue his winning ways off a flying 24.73 success at this track. Expecting another bold showing. CUMBRIA BENNY (7) comes off a big run when finishing third in a slick 24.90 last time. Has claims on that run.
